
Project Name: Coinwatch Extension  
Product Owner: Abolfazl Rafsanjani  
Product Manager:Fatemeh Zarehzadeh  
Scrum Master: Shahrokh Khayam  
Sprint Duration:2 weeks  

### Epic 1: Coin Table

User Story 1:
As a user, I want to have technical analysis for total market status of sell or buy.  
Acceptance Criteria:
- Users see technical analysis for total.

User Story 2: 
As a user, I want to be able to see the list of top 5 digital currencies based on price through the extension.  
Acceptance Criteria: 
- Users can filter coins by value and sort by various criteria.

User Story 3:
As a user, I want to be able to view detailed information about each currency by clicking on each.  
Acceptance Criteria: 
- Users clicking on a currency opens a detailed table with a description.

### Epic 2: Search Box

User Story 4: 
As a user, I want to be able to search digital currencies.  
Acceptance Criteria:
- Users can search coins by writing their name.

### Epic 3: Conversion Box

User Story 5:
As a user, I want to be able to get the latest conversion rates for popular cryptocurrencies, like Bitcoin, Ethereum, Cardano, Solana, Dogecoin, and others.  
Acceptance Criteria: 
- Have a conversion box.

User Story 6:
As a user, I want to be able to view comments and reply to other users.  
Acceptance Criteria:
- Users can view comments and express their opinions by referring to the comments section.

### Epic 5: Performance/Design Optimization and Updates

User Story 7: 
As a user, I want digital currencies to be updated and displayed in real-time.  
Acceptance Criteria:
- A suitable implementation for updating the information of digital currencies.

User Story 8: 
As a user, I want the extension to be user-friendly and perform smoothly.  
Acceptance Criteria:
- Page load times are optimized.
- The design should be user-friendly.
User Story 9: 
As a user, I want to be able to activate light mode and dark mode in the settings.  
Acceptance Criteria:
- Add setting options.
- Ability to switch between light/dark mode.

### Epic 6: Pages

User Story 10: 
As a user, I want to view the page with any desired theme.  
Acceptance Criteria: 
- Users can turn it on or off with the theme change button.


User Story 11: 
As a user, I want to have a list of my favorite currencies pinned.
Acceptance Criteria: 
- User can pin their favorite
